@node intro "df_lib - Introduction"
@{line}
@{b}Introduction@{ub}
@{line}
@{line}
df_lib is a library for the Amiga version of PureBasic. It currently supports shift operations (e.g. LSL and LSR) and timer routines.
@{line}
@endnode

